Compatible with iOS 11

A tweak for Instagram app to enable/ensure the newest emojis that Instagram has included to the sticker feature.
For example: (Supposing) iOS 12.1 jailbroken + Instagram 72.0 (that has yet to include iOS 12.1 emojis) to get iOS 12.1 emoji stickers

This also works with PoomSmart's EmojiPort tweak, as it will replace the current emoji stickers with the ones offered by that tweak.
For example: iOS 11.3 jailbroken + EmojiPort + Instagram 72.0 to get iOS 12.1 emoji stickers

No options to configure.
